cp|8|AT|

^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|If you make a minor raise (to either the 2 level or 3 level), you are guaranteed to have no 4 card major. That is the most important thing to remember. If you raise your partner's minor, you are giving up on finding a major suit fit.|
