- Now, what if there is an intervening bid such as an overcall or a double?|
PG| ***** 161 ***** |


cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Inverted minors are off in competition (including over takeout and doubles), in the sense that a raise to 2 is less than a limit raise. A raise to 3 is still preemptive. |
