cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The same thing applies over 1 of a minor. With 10+, you redouble with less than 4 card support, and bid 2N (Jordan) with 4+ card support. However, the other thing to keep in mind is that the modern treatment is to play 1 level responses are forcing over a takeout double. Therefore, with 10+, responder can also bid a new suit at the one level, rather than redoubling, if that is a better bid. 

